	<div class="entry entry-0">
		<div class="entrytitle">
			<h2><a href="http://www.insidefacebook.com/2007/12/09/inside-facebook-marketing-bible-24-ways-to-market-your-brand-company-product-or-service-in-facebook/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to The Facebook Marketing Bible: 24 Ways to Market Your Brand, Company, Product, or Service Inside Facebook">The Facebook Marketing Bible: 24 Ways to Market Your Brand, Company, Product, or Service Inside Facebook</a></h2> 
			<h3>December 9th, 2007</h3>
		</div>


<div style="border-bottom:1px dotted #4F5158;color:#999999;font-size:12px;padding:5px;">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td valign="middle" style="padding-right:20px;">

 By Justin Smith
</td><td valign="middle" style="padding-right:20px;">

 <a href="http://www.insidefacebook.com/2007/12/09/inside-facebook-marketing-bible-24-ways-to-market-your-brand-company-product-or-service-in-facebook/#comments" class="commentslink"  title="Comment on The Facebook Marketing Bible: 24 Ways to Market Your Brand, Company, Product, or Service Inside Facebook">206 Comments &#187;</a>
</td><td valign="middle" style="padding-right:20px;">

